---
layout: base.njk
title: ブログ — 記銘帖
nav: blog
permalink: /blog/
---
<div class="section-label">BLOG</div>
<p class="section-index">不定期更新</p>

{% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
<div class="post">
  <p class="post-meta">{{ post.data.date | ym }}</p>
  <p class="post-title"><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></p>
  <div class="post-body">{{ post.data.excerpt or "" }}</div>
</div>
{% endfor %}
